/**\n * Sorts expressions in char class in the following order:\n * - meta chars
column2: ordered alphabetically by value\n * - chars (except `control` kind) and class ranges
column3: ordered alphabetically (`from` char is used for class ranges)\n * - if ambiguous
column4: class range comes before char\n * - if ambiguous between two class ranges
column5: orders alphabetically by `to` char\n * - control chars
column6:
ordered alphabetically by value
 * @param {Object} a - Left Char or ClassRange node
 * @param {Object} b - Right Char or ClassRange node
 * @returns {number}
 */Comment.Multiline
